Package: SpatAggNet
Type: Package
Title: A package in support of the manuscript "Spatial aggregation confounds 
    null model-based inference of species association networks"
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Andrew J. Rominger
Description: Evaluating the possibility that chance alone can lead to 
    association network connections without any real ecological association 
    between species
